name: Wrinkly Studio Lights
description:
Ever wondered how your passport photo will look light in 30 years? What about that forehead wrinkles treatment cream you are using every night, are you sure you need it? Fear you not, this TI may save you lots of $$$ in cosmetics and photo booth charges.

It works particularly well for img2img. Let's say you want a picture of yourself. In this case you'd txt2img prompt something like

a close up photo portrait of a man with a serious look on his face

(obviously) resulting in

now let's switch to img2img and prompt (here I'm using denoising ~0.5)

a close up photo portrait of a man with a serious look on his face, wrinklystudiolights1

this will unleash the full power of this TI and travel through time to bring back...

amazing, isn't it? Look at those marked wrinkles, white hairs and catchy catchlights!

The TI is quite strong (possibly overfitted), so you may want to tune it down a bit as [wrinklystudiolights1]
